title: Marianne Williamson Interview
itunes:title: Marianne Williamson Interview
description:
Today on the show we had presidential candidate and New York Times best seller Marianna Williamson where she spoke about her new book, presidential debate and more. Also, Charlamagne  gave "Donkey of the Day" to a mother and daughter that just wanted some sea food and Angela Yee helped some listeners out during "Ask Yee".
